{{italic title}} '''''Review of International Law and Politics''''' (Turkish: ''Uluslararası Hukuk ve Politika'') is a quarterly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[law journal]] that was established in 2004. It is published by the [[International Strategic Research Organization]].
